   "type": "text",
   "x": 40,
   "y": 320,
   "width": 1855.98,
   "height": 15,
   "text": "Termix drives guacd over TCP 4822 and reaches nine reachable hosts with one reusable Ed25519 identity, grouped into four folders. The four Proxmox nodes only connected after a narrow Datacenter firewall IPSet allowed TCP 22 from the Termix host alone; ten unreachable targets stayed out.",
   "originalText": "Termix drives guacd over TCP 4822 and reaches nine reachable hosts with one reusable Ed25519 identity, grouped into four folders. The four Proxmox nodes only connected after a narrow Datacenter firewall IPSet allowed TCP 22 from the Termix host alone; ten unreachable targets stayed out.",
